Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.obo.mpo

Class MpAnnotationParser

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.obo.mpo.MpAnnotationParser
public class MpAnnotationParser extends Object
Class to parse the following files from the MGI site. 1. MGI_GenePheno.rpt (for now, omit MGI_PhenoGenoMP.rpt). 2. MGI_Pheno_Sex.rpt MGI_Pheno_Sex.rpt has a subset of the same models as MGI_GenePheno but additionally adds information on whether the phenotypes were sex-specific. This class allows users to parse either each individual model (MpSimpleModel or to combine the models according to gene (MpGeneModel.
Author:
Hannah Blau, Peter Robinson
